  "response": "Here are some baby boy names that start with \"Bh\":\n\n1. **Bhavin** - A name of Indian origin meaning \"brilliant\" or \"illuminated.\"\n2. **Bhagav** - Derived from Sanskrit, meaning \"fortunate\" or \"divine.\"\n3. **Bhaskar** - A Sanskrit name meaning \"sun\" or \"light.\"\n4. **Bhuvan** - A name meaning \"the world\" or \"earth\" in Sanskrit.\n5. **Bhumi** - While traditionally more common for girls, it can be adapted as a unisex name meaning \"earth.\"\n\nThese names are culturally rich and have positive meanings. If you\u2019re looking for additional options or variations, feel free to ask!",
